node.text:
This year has been challenging, life changing, and one we will never forget! Cheers to a new year full of health, hope, peace, and joy🥂❤️

2 winners will get a $100 shop credit for them + a friend!

How to enter:
1- Like + save this post
2- tag a friend below and write what you wish them for the next year. You can tag as many friends as you’d like, each separate tag is another entry!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by mushie in Houston, Texas.

node.text:
🧶Want to win a knit blanket?
Soft organic cotton for your little one! Share this post to your stories, tag us, and comment below your weekend plans when you’re done!

Winner announced Tuesday!
Open worldwide 😘

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by mushie in Houston, Texas. May be an image of 1 person, baby and indoor.

node.text:
Did you know we’re also in-store at some Nordstrom locations? Send us a picture if you’ve seen our products there🎉
Head over to the previous post if you want to win a @mushie bundle❤️

node.text:
🌸GIVEAWAY🌸
Our snack cups are now available at @nordstrom and we’re so excited!
2 comments will win a @mushie bundle!

Tag mama friends below in separate comments, and tell them we’re at Nordstrom!
Each tag = another entry, so tag away!

You can also find our bibs, clips, teethers, pacifier case, and stacking cups there! And another item will launch there soon! Can you guess?

Winner announced Tuesday 🥰
GOOD LUCK!
